0.3.1 (Jan. 16, 2017): Fix wxWidgets errors.

0.3.1 (Sept. 18 2010): Minor bug fix release.  Fixes a number of crashes and adds the ability to switch which camera is used.  Also now saves location of last scan for easier file-system navigation.

0.3 (Summer 2010): Removed requirement for USB-based laser movement.  Added on-screen feedback for where the laser appears.  Substantially improved vibration and movement robustness.

0.2 (Fall 2009): Substantial improvement in accuracy by moving from a calibration-only method to a reference-pixel method.  Enabled .ply output.

0.1 (Fall 2008): Original version.
